(2, 'Red Notice', 'An Interpol-issued Red Notice is a global alert to hunt and capture the world’s most wanted. But when a daring heist brings together the FBI’s top profiler (Johnson) and two rival criminals (Gadot, Reynolds), there’s no telling what will happen', 'An Interpol-issued Red Notice is a global alert to hunt and capture the world’s most wanted. But when a daring heist brings together the FBI’s top profiler (Johnson) and two rival criminals (Gadot, Reynolds), there’s no telling what will happen', 2023, 1, 4, 1, '[\"576\",\"1066\",\"1159\"]', '4', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Pj0wz7zu3Ms', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Pj0wz7zu3Ms', '9067'),
(3, 'The Shawshank Redemption', 'Framed in the 1940s for the double murder of his wife and her lover, u', 'Framed in the 1940s for the double murder of his wife and her lover, upstanding banker Andy Dufresne begins a new life at the Shawshank prison, where he puts his accounting skills to work for an amoral warden. During his long stretch in prison, Dufresne comes to be admired by the other inmates -- including an older prisoner named Red -- for his integrity and unquenchable sense of hope.', 1994, 1, 5, 2, '[\"7\", \"8\", \"9\"]', '3', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PLl99DlL6b4', '', '8520'),
(4, 'The Godfather Part II', 'In the continuing saga of the Corleone crime family, a young Vito Corl', 'In the continuing saga of the Corleone crime family, a young Vito Corleone grows up in Sicily and in 1910s New York. In the 1950s, Michael Corleone attempts to expand the family business into Las Vegas, Hollywood and Cuba.', 1974, 1, 5, 2, '[\"5\", \"10\", \"11\"]', '2', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rcU6DUUUd7k', '', '12120'),
(5, 'Dilwale Dulhania Le Jayenge', 'Raj is a rich, carefree, happy-go-lucky second generation NRI. Simran ', 'Raj is a rich, carefree, happy-go-lucky second generation NRI. Simran is the daughter of Chaudhary Baldev Singh, who in spite of being an NRI is very strict about adherence to Indian values. Simran has left for India to be married to her childhood fianc?. Raj leaves for India with a mission at his hands, to claim his lady love under the noses of her whole family. Thus begins a saga.', 1995, 2, 5, 3, '[\"12\", \"13\", \"14\"]', '4', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oIZ4U21DRlM', '', '11400'),
(6, 'Schindler\'s List', 'The true story of how businessman Oskar Schindler saved over a thousan', 'The true story of how businessman Oskar Schindler saved over a thousand Jewish lives from the Nazis while they worked as slaves in his factory during World War II.', 1993, 1, 5, 2, '[\"15\", \"16\", \"17\"]', '5', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mxphAlJID9U', 'http://www.schindlerslist.com/', '11700'),
(7, 'Spirited Away', 'A young girl, Chihiro, becomes trapped in a strange new world of spiri', 'A young girl, Chihiro, becomes trapped in a strange new world of spirits. When her parents undergo a mysterious transformation, she must call upon the courage she never knew she had to free her family.', 2001, 3, 5, 4, '[\"18\", \"19\", \"20\"]', '6', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ByXuk9QqQkk', 'http://movies.disney.com/spirited-away', '7500'),
(8, '12 Angry Men', 'The defense and the prosecution have rested and the jury is filing int', 'The defense and the prosecution have rested and the jury is filing into the jury room to decide if a young Spanish-American is guilty or innocent of murdering his father. What begins as an open and shut case soon becomes a mini-drama of each of the jurors\' prejudices and preconceptions about the trial, the accused, and each other.', 1957, 1, 5, 2, '[\"21\", \"22\", \"23\"]', '7', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TEN-2uTi2c0', '', '5820'),
(9, 'Your Name.', 'High schoolers Mitsuha and Taki are complete strangers living separate', 'High schoolers Mitsuha and Taki are complete strangers living separate lives. But one night, they suddenly switch places. Mitsuha wakes up in Taki?s body, and he in hers. This bizarre occurrence continues to happen randomly, and the two must adjust their lives around each other.', 2016, 3, 5, 5, '[\"24\", \"25\", \"26\"]', '8', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_oWzYOwXn-o', 'https://www.funimationfilms.com/movie/yourname/', '6360'),
(10, 'Parasite', 'All unemployed, Ki-taek\'s family takes peculiar interest in the wealth', 'All unemployed, Ki-taek\'s family takes peculiar interest in the wealthy and glamorous Parks for their livelihood until they get entangled in an unexpected incident.', 2019, 4, 5, 3, '[\"27\", \"28\", \"29\"]', '9', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tBfgTZsBeFM', 'https://www.parasite-movie.com/', '7980'),
(11, 'The Green Mile', 'A supernatural tale set on death row in a Southern prison, where gentl', 'A supernatural tale set on death row in a Southern prison, where gentle giant John Coffey possesses the mysterious power to heal people\'s ailments. When the cell block\'s head guard, Paul Edgecomb, recognizes Coffey\'s miraculous gift, he tries desperately to help stave off the condemned man\'s execution.', 1999, 1, 5, 6, '[\"30\", \"31\", \"32\"]', '3', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Bg7epsq0OIQ', 'http://thegreenmile.warnerbros.com/', '11340'),
(12, 'The Dark Knight', 'Batman raises the stakes in his war on crime. With the help of Lt. Jim', 'Batman raises the stakes in his war on crime. With the help of Lt. Jim Gordon and District Attorney Harvey Dent, Batman sets out to dismantle the remaining criminal organizations that plague the streets. The partnership proves to be effective, but they soon find themselves prey to a reign of chaos unleashed by a rising criminal mastermind known to the terrified citizens of Gotham as the Joker.', 2008, 5, 5, 2, '[\"33\", \"34\", \"35\"]', '10', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kmJLuwP3MbY', 'https://www.warnerbros.com/movies/dark-knight/', '9120'),
(13, 'Cuando Sea Joven', '70-year-old Malena gets a second chance at life when she magically tur', '70-year-old Malena gets a second chance at life when she magically turns into her 22-year-old self. Now, posing as \"Maria\" to hide her true identity, she becomes the lead singer of her grandson\'s band and tries to recover her dream of singing, which she had to give up at some point.', 2022, 6, 5, 3, '[\"36\", \"37\", \"38\"]', '11', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4EXETqcw-k8', 'https://videocine.com.mx/peliculas/cuando-sea-joven/', '6900'),
(14, 'Pulp Fiction', 'A burger-loving hit man, his philosophical partner, a drug-addled gang', 'A burger-loving hit man, his philosophical partner, a drug-addled gangster\'s moll and a washed-up boxer converge in this sprawling, comedic crime caper. Their adventures unfurl in three stories that ingeniously trip back and forth in time.', 1994, 1, 5, 7, '[\"39\", \"40\", \"41\"]', '12', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tGpTpVyI_OQ', 'https://www.miramax.com/movie/pulp-fiction/', '9240'),
(15, 'Forrest Gump', 'A man with a low IQ has accomplished great things in his life and been', 'A man with a low IQ has accomplished great things in his life and been present during significant historic events?in each case, far exceeding what anyone imagined he could do. But despite all he has achieved, his one true love eludes him.', 1994, 1, 5, 3, '[\"30\", \"42\", \"43\"]', '13', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=76WeEuR0qk4', 'https://www.paramountmovies.com/movies/forrest-gump', '8520'),
(16, 'The Good, the Bad and the Ugly', 'While the Civil War rages on between the Union and the Confederacy, th', 'While the Civil War rages on between the Union and the Confederacy, three men ? a quiet loner, a ruthless hitman, and a Mexican bandit ? comb the American Southwest in search of a strongbox containing $200,000 in stolen gold.', 1966, 1, 5, 8, '[\"44\", \"45\", \"46\"]', '14', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IFNUGzCOQoI', 'http://www.mgm.com/#/our-titles/766/The-Good,-the-Bad-and-the-Ugly', '9660'),
(17, 'The Lord of the Rings: The Return of the King', 'Aragorn is revealed as the heir to the ancient kings as he, Gandalf an', 'Aragorn is revealed as the heir to the ancient kings as he, Gandalf and the other members of the broken fellowship struggle to save Gondor from Sauron\'s forces. Meanwhile, Frodo and Sam take the ring closer to the heart of Mordor, the dark lord\'s realm.', 2003, 7, 5, 9, '[\"47\", \"48\", \"49\"]', '15', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zckJCxYxn1g', 'http://www.lordoftherings.net', '12060'),
(18, 'Primal: Tales of Savagery', 'Genndy Tartakovsky\'s Primal: Tales of Savagery features a caveman and ', 'Genndy Tartakovsky\'s Primal: Tales of Savagery features a caveman and a dinosaur on the brink of extinction. Bonded by tragedy, this unlikely friendship becomes the only hope of survival.', 2019, 1, 5, 1, '[\"50\",\"51\",\"52\"]', '16', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vaOn8koDa9E', '', '5100'),
(19, 'GoodFellas', 'The true story of Henry Hill, a half-Irish, half-Sicilian Brooklyn kid', 'The true story of Henry Hill, a half-Irish, half-Sicilian Brooklyn kid who is adopted by neighbourhood gangsters at an early age and climbs the ranks of a Mafia family under the guidance of Jimmy Conway.', 1990, 1, 5, 2, '[\"53\", \"54\", \"55\"]', '17', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PTBRNXGQR9Q', 'http://www.warnerbros.com/goodfellas', '8700'),
(20, 'Cinema Paradiso', 'A filmmaker recalls his childhood, when he fell in love with the movie', 'A filmmaker recalls his childhood, when he fell in love with the movies at his village\'s theater and formed a deep friendship with the theater\'s projectionist.', 1988, 8, 5, 2, '[\"56\", \"57\", \"58\"]', '18', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JMyVSD6OvO8', '', '7440'),
(21, 'Seven Samurai', 'A samurai answers a village\'s request for protection after he falls on', 'A samurai answers a village\'s request for protection after he falls on hard times. The town needs protection from bandits, so the samurai gathers six others to help him teach the people how to defend themselves, and the villagers provide the soldiers with food.', 2023, 3, 5, 1, '[\"59\",\"60\",\"61\"]', '19', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5dZioLIejeo', '', '12420'),
(22, 'Dou kyu sei ? Classmates', 'Rihito Sajo, an honor student with a perfect score on the entrance exa', 'Rihito Sajo, an honor student with a perfect score on the entrance exam and Hikaru Kusakabe, in a band and popular among girls, would have never crossed paths. Until one day they started talking at the practice for their school?s upcoming chorus festival. After school, the two meet regularly, as Hikaru helps Rihito to improve his singing skills. While they listen to each other?s voice and harmonize, their hearts start to beat together.', 2016, 3, 5, 5, '[\"62\", \"63\", \"64\"]', '20', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wFQTncSyukA', 'http://doukyuseimovie.com/', '3660'),
(23, 'Gabriel\'s Inferno', 'An intriguing and sinful exploration of seduction, forbidden love, and', 'An intriguing and sinful exploration of seduction, forbidden love, and redemption, Gabriel\'s Inferno is a captivating and wildly passionate tale of one man\'s escape from his own personal hell as he tries to earn the impossible--forgiveness and love.', 2020, 1, 5, 5, '[\"65\", \"66\", \"67\"]', '21', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kgWFjmiqHmQ', 'https://watch.passionflix.com/watch/fc15dc25-cf48-4d4f-aa8e-9afb032233cc', '7320'),
(24, 'The Legend of Hei', 'When cat spirit Luo Xiaohei\'s home is deforested by humans, he must fi', 'When cat spirit Luo Xiaohei\'s home is deforested by humans, he must find a new one. He runs into a group of other spirit creatures who take him under their wing with dreams of reconquering the land they say is rightfully theirs. However, they run into a human known as Wuxian who separates Luo Xiaohei from the other spirits and the two go on a journey, with the cat spirit learning to control his abilities as well as forming his own thoughts on whether or not he should ally with the spirits or the humans.', 2019, 9, 5, 4, '[\"68\", \"69\", \"70\"]', '22', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ps0O9l2CvOM', 'https://luoxiaohei-movie.com/', '6120'),
(25, 'Life Is Beautiful', 'A touching story of an Italian book seller of Jewish ancestry who live', 'A touching story of an Italian book seller of Jewish ancestry who lives in his own little fairy tale. His creative and happy life would come to an abrupt halt when his entire family is deported to a concentration camp during World War II. While locked up he tries to convince his son that the whole thing is just a game.', 1997, 10, 5, 3, '[\"71\", \"72\", \"73\"]', '23', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pAYEQP8gx3w', '', '6960'),
(26, 'Grave of the Fireflies', 'In the final months of World War II, 14-year-old Seita and his sister ', 'In the final months of World War II, 14-year-old Seita and his sister Setsuko are orphaned when their mother is killed during an air raid in Kobe, Japan. After a falling out with their aunt, they move into an abandoned bomb shelter. With no surviving relatives and their emergency rations depleted, Seita and Setsuko struggle to survive.', 1988, 3, 5, 4, '[\"74\", \"75\", \"76\"]', '24', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4vPeTSRd580', '', '5340'),
(27, 'The Boy, the Mole, the Fox and the Horse', 'The unlikely friendship of a boy, a mole, a fox and a horse traveling ', 'The unlikely friendship of a boy, a mole, a fox and a horse traveling together in the boy?s search for home.', 2022, 5, 5, 4, '[\"77\", \"78\", \"79\"]', '25', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=609A7IGdoEc', 'https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/m001gn7t', '2040'),
(28, 'Psycho', 'When larcenous real estate clerk Marion Crane goes on the lam with a w', 'When larcenous real estate clerk Marion Crane goes on the lam with a wad of cash and hopes of starting a new life, she ends up at the notorious Bates Motel, where manager Norman Bates cares for his housebound mother.', 1960, 1, 5, 10, '[\"80\", \"81\", \"82\"]', '26', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=D90QhegiVvo', '', '6540'),
(29, 'Once Upon a Time in America', 'A former Prohibition-era Jewish gangster returns to the Lower East Sid', 'A former Prohibition-era Jewish gangster returns to the Lower East Side of Manhattan over thirty years later, where he once again must confront the ghosts and regrets of his old life.', 1984, 1, 5, 2, '[\"54\", \"83\", \"84\"]', '14', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_gdEuuxW-zk', '', '13740'),
(30, 'Gabriel\'s Inferno: Part II', 'Professor Gabriel Emerson finally learns the truth about Julia Mitchel', 'Professor Gabriel Emerson finally learns the truth about Julia Mitchell\'s identity, but his realization comes a moment too late. Julia is done waiting for the well-respected Dante specialist to remember her and wants nothing more to do with him. Can Gabriel win back her heart before she finds love in another\'s arms?', 2020, 6, 5, 5, '[\"65\", \"66\", \"85\"]', '21', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5g02v1oz5Y0', 'https://watch.passionflix.com/watch/f299fa17-5a2b-4fee-b53a-a4651747431b', '6300'),
(31, 'Fight Club', 'A ticking-time-bomb insomniac and a slippery soap salesman channel pri', 'A ticking-time-bomb insomniac and a slippery soap salesman channel primal male aggression into a shocking new form of therapy. Their concept catches on, with underground \"fight clubs\" forming in every town, until an eccentric gets in the way and ignites an out-of-control spiral toward oblivion.', 1999, 1, 5, 2, '[\"86\", \"87\", \"88\"]', '27', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6JnN1DmbqoU', 'http://www.foxmovies.com/movies/fight-club', '8340'),
(32, 'Impossible Things', 'Matilde is a woman who, after the death of her husband - a man who con', 'Matilde is a woman who, after the death of her husband - a man who constantly abused her - finds her new best friend in Miguel, her young, insecure, disoriented and even dealer neighbor', 2021, 11, 5, 11, '[\"89\", \"90\", \"91\"]', '28', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eRJryexKYxQ', '', '5280'),
(33, 'City of God', 'In the slums of Rio, two kids\' paths diverge as one struggles to becom', 'In the slums of Rio, two kids\' paths diverge as one struggles to become a photographer and the other a kingpin.', 2002, 12, 5, 2, '[\"92\", \"93\", \"94\"]', '29', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_mDvXaRJcTM', 'http://cidadededeus.globo.com/', '7800'),
(34, 'One Flew Over the Cuckoo\'s Nest', 'A petty criminal fakes insanity to serve his sentence in a mental ward', 'A petty criminal fakes insanity to serve his sentence in a mental ward rather than prison. He soon finds himself as a leader to the other patients?and an enemy to the cruel, domineering nurse who runs the ward.', 1975, 1, 5, 2, '[\"95\", \"96\", \"97\"]', '30', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3NSVJlBeGBA', '', '7980'),
(35, 'Gabriel\'s Inferno: Part III', 'The final part of the film adaption of the erotic romance novel Gabrie', 'The final part of the film adaption of the erotic romance novel Gabriel\'s Inferno written by an anonymous Canadian author under the pen name Sylvain Reynard.', 2020, 1, 5, 5, '[\"65\", \"66\", \"98\"]', '21', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mjPUGem9SaY', '', '6300'),
(36, 'Harakiri', 'Down-on-his-luck veteran Tsugumo Hanshiro enters the courtyard of the ', 'Down-on-his-luck veteran Tsugumo Hanshiro enters the courtyard of the prosperous House of Iyi. Unemployed, and with no family, he hopes to find a place to commit seppuku?and a worthy second to deliver the coup de gr?ce in his suicide ritual. The senior counselor for the Iyi clan questions the ronin?s resolve and integrity, suspecting Hanshiro of seeking charity rather than an honorable end. What follows is a pair of interlocking stories which lay bare the difference between honor and respect, and promises to examine the legendary foundations of the Samurai code.', 2023, 3, 5, 1, '[\"99\",\"100\",\"101\"]', '31', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gfABwM-Ppng', '', '8100'),
(37, 'The Quintessential Quintuplets Movie', 'When five lovely young girls who hate studying hire part-time tutor Fu', 'When five lovely young girls who hate studying hire part-time tutor Futaro, he guides not only their education but also their hearts. Time spent has brought them all closer, with feelings growing within the girls and Futaro. As they finish their third year of high school and their last school festival approaches, they set their sights on what?s next. Is there a future with one of them and Futaro?', 2022, 3, 5, 4, '[\"102\", \"103\", \"104\"]', '32', 1, 0, '', 'https://www.thequintessentialquintuplets-movie.com', '8160'),
(38, 'Interstellar', 'The adventures of a group of explorers who make use of a newly discove', 'The adventures of a group of explorers who make use of a newly discovered wormhole to surpass the limitations on human space travel and conquer the vast distances involved in an interstellar voyage.', 2014, 5, 5, 9, '[\"105\", \"106\", \"107\"]', '10', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0vxOhd4qlnA', 'http://www.interstellarmovie.net/', '10140'),
(39, 'Spider-Man: Into the Spider-Verse', 'Miles Morales is juggling his life between being a high school student', 'Miles Morales is juggling his life between being a high school student and being a spider-man. When Wilson \"Kingpin\" Fisk uses a super collider, others from across the Spider-Verse are transported to this dimension.', 2018, 1, 5, 1, '[\"1\",\"2\",\"108\"]', '33', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tg52up16eq0', 'https://www.sonypictures.com/movies/spidermanintothespiderverse', '7020'),
(40, 'Howl\'s Moving Castle', 'Sophie, a young milliner is turned into an elderly woman by a witch wh', 'Sophie, a young milliner is turned into an elderly woman by a witch who enters her shop and curses her. She encounters a wizard named Howl and gets caught up in his resistance to fighting for the king.', 2004, 3, 5, 6, '[\"109\", \"110\", \"111\"]', '6', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iwROgK94zcM', 'https://howlugokueiga.seesaa.net/', '7140'),
(41, 'The Lord of the Rings: The Fellowship of the Ring', 'Young hobbit Frodo Baggins, after inheriting a mysterious ring from hi', 'Young hobbit Frodo Baggins, after inheriting a mysterious ring from his uncle Bilbo, must leave his home in order to keep it from falling into the hands of its evil creator. Along the way, a fellowship is formed to protect the ringbearer and make sure that the ring arrives at its final destination: Mt. Doom, the only place where it can be destroyed.', 2001, 7, 5, 9, '[\"47\", \"49\", \"112\"]', '15', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_nZdmwHrcnw', 'http://www.lordoftherings.net/', '10740'),
(42, 'A Silent Voice: The Movie', 'Shouya Ishida starts bullying the new girl in class, Shouko Nishimiya,', 'Shouya Ishida starts bullying the new girl in class, Shouko Nishimiya, because she is deaf. But as the teasing continues, the rest of the class starts to turn on Shouya for his lack of compassion. When they leave elementary school, Shouko and Shouya do not speak to each other again... until an older, wiser Shouya, tormented by his past behaviour, decides he must see Shouko once more. He wants to atone for his sins, but is it already too late...?', 2016, 3, 5, 4, '[\"19\", \"113\", \"114\"]', '34', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=e8tMQVwqj54', 'http://asilentvoice.com.au/', '7800'),
(43, 'The Empire Strikes Back', 'The epic saga continues as Luke Skywalker, in hopes of defeating the e', 'The epic saga continues as Luke Skywalker, in hopes of defeating the evil Galactic Empire, learns the ways of the Jedi from aging master Yoda. But Darth Vader is more determined than ever to capture Luke. Meanwhile, rebel leader Princess Leia, cocky Han Solo, Chewbacca, and droids C-3PO and R2-D2 are thrown into various stages of capture, betrayal and despair.', 1980, 1, 5, 9, '[\"115\", \"116\", \"117\"]', '35', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vU6L3jXt2r8', 'http://www.starwars.com/films/star-wars-episode-v-the-empire-strikes-back', '7440'),
(44, 'My Fault', 'Noah must leave her city, boyfriend, and friends to move into William ', 'Noah must leave her city, boyfriend, and friends to move into William Leister\'s mansion, the flashy and wealthy husband of her mother Rafaela. As a proud and independent 17 year old, Noah resists living in a mansion surrounded by luxury. However, it is there where she meets Nick, her new stepbrother, and the clash of their strong personalities becomes evident from the very beginning.', 2023, 13, 5, 5, '[\"118\", \"119\", \"120\"]', '36', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PaB7cGBuCP0', '', '7020'),
(45, 'Hotarubi no Mori e', 'One hot summer day a little girl gets lost in an enchanted forest of t', 'One hot summer day a little girl gets lost in an enchanted forest of the mountain god where spirits reside. A young boy appears before her, but she cannot touch him for fear of making him disappear. And so a wondrous adventure awaits...', 2011, 3, 5, 5, '[\"121\", \"122\", \"123\"]', '37', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qXLSRH31Yao', '', '2700'),
(46, 'A Dog\'s Will', 'The lively Jo?o Grilo and the sly Chic? are poor guys living in the hi', 'The lively Jo?o Grilo and the sly Chic? are poor guys living in the hinterland who cheat a bunch of people in a small in Northeastern Brazil. When they die, they have to be judged by Christ, the Devil and the Virgin Mary before they are admitted to paradise.', 2000, 12, 5, 3, '[\"124\", \"125\", \"126\"]', '38', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wDVdgnhiNlY', '', '6240'),
(47, 'The Pianist', 'The true story of pianist Wladyslaw Szpilman\'s experiences in Warsaw d', 'The true story of pianist Wladyslaw Szpilman\'s experiences in Warsaw during the Nazi occupation. When the Jews of the city find themselves forced into a ghetto, Szpilman finds work playing in a caf?; and when his family is deported in 1942, he stays behind, works for a while as a laborer, and eventually goes into hiding in the ruins of the war-torn city.', 2002, 8, 5, 2, '[\"127\", \"128\", \"129\"]', '39', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BFwGqLa_oAo', 'http://www.thepianistmovie.com/', '9000'),
(48, 'Hope', 'After 8-year-old So-won narrowly survives a brutal sexual assault, her', 'After 8-year-old So-won narrowly survives a brutal sexual assault, her family labors to help her heal while coping with their own rage and grief.', 2013, 4, 5, 2, '[\"130\",\"131\",\"132\"]', '40', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9PsBBsX6TC0', '', '7320'),
(49, 'The Lord of the Rings: The Two Towers', 'Frodo and Sam are trekking to Mordor to destroy the One Ring of Power ', 'Frodo and Sam are trekking to Mordor to destroy the One Ring of Power while Gimli, Legolas and Aragorn search for the orc-captured Merry and Pippin. All along, nefarious wizard Saruman awaits the Fellowship members at the Orthanc Tower in Isengard.', 2002, 7, 5, 9, '[\"112\", \"47\", \"48\"]', '15', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nuTU5XcZTLA', 'http://www.lordoftherings.net/', '10740'),
(50, 'Whiplash', 'Under the direction of a ruthless instructor, a talented young drummer', 'Under the direction of a ruthless instructor, a talented young drummer begins to pursue perfection at any cost, even his humanity.', 2014, 1, 5, 2, '[\"133\",\"134\",\"135\"]', '41', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Df1xkYYbYrY', 'http://sonyclassics.com/whiplash/', '6420'),
(51, 'Taylor Swift: Reputation Stadium Tour', 'Taylor Swift takes the stage in Dallas for the Reputation Stadium Tour', 'Taylor Swift takes the stage in Dallas for the Reputation Stadium Tour and celebrates a monumental night of music, memories and visual magic.', 2018, 1, 5, 12, '[\"136\", \"137\", \"138\"]', '42', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HIb_TlK2HAI', 'https://www.netflix.com/title/81026251', '7500'),
(52, 'Se7en', 'Two homicide detectives are on a desperate hunt for a serial killer wh', 'Two homicide detectives are on a desperate hunt for a serial killer whose crimes are based on the \"seven deadly sins\" in this dark and haunting film that takes viewers from the tortured remains of one victim to the next. The seasoned Det. Sommerset researches each sin in an effort to get inside the killer\'s mind, while his novice partner, Mills, scoffs at his efforts to unravel the case.', 1995, 1, 5, 13, '[\"87\", \"8\", \"139\"]', '27', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SpKbZ_3zlb0', 'http://www.sevenmovie.com/', '7620'),
(53, 'Josee, the Tiger and the Fish', 'With dreams of diving abroad, Tsuneo gets a job assisting Josee, an ar', 'With dreams of diving abroad, Tsuneo gets a job assisting Josee, an artist whose imagination takes her far beyond her wheelchair. But when the tide turns against them, they push each other to places they never thought possible, and inspire a love fit for a storybook.', 2020, 3, 5, 4, '[\"140\", \"141\", \"142\"]', '43', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hLEjE77PbcA', 'https://joseetora.jp/', '5880'),
(54, 'Inception', 'Cobb, a skilled thief who commits corporate espionage by infiltrating ', 'Cobb, a skilled thief who commits corporate espionage by infiltrating the subconscious of his targets is offered a chance to regain his old life as payment for a task considered to be impossible: \"inception\", the implantation of another person\'s idea into a target\'s subconscious.', 2010, 5, 5, 1, '[\"143\",\"144\",\"145\"]', '10', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JE9z-gy4De4', 'https://www.warnerbros.com/movies/inception', '8880'),
(55, 'Rear Window', 'A wheelchair-bound photographer spies on his neighbors from his apartm', 'A wheelchair-bound photographer spies on his neighbors from his apartment window and becomes convinced one of them has committed murder.', 1954, 1, 5, 7, '[\"146\", \"147\", \"148\"]', '26', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iZOTTxwzyMU', '', '6720'),
(56, 'Sunset Boulevard', 'A hack screenwriter writes a screenplay for a former silent film star ', 'A hack screenwriter writes a screenplay for a former silent film star who has faded into Hollywood obscurity.', 2023, 1, 5, 2, '[\"149\",\"150\",\"151\"]', '44', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=USv1hJTlbhg', '', '6600'),
(57, 'Ikiru', 'Kanji Watanabe is a middle-aged man who has worked in the same monoton', 'Kanji Watanabe is a middle-aged man who has worked in the same monotonous bureaucratic position for decades. Learning he has cancer, he starts to look for the meaning of his life.', 2023, 3, 5, 2, '[\"60\",\"152\",\"153\"]', '19', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2VeLN3IDjzQ', '', '8580'),
(58, 'American History X', 'Derek Vineyard is paroled after serving 3 years in prison for killing ', 'Derek Vineyard is paroled after serving 3 years in prison for killing two African-American men. Through his brother, Danny Vineyard\'s narration, we learn that before going to prison, Derek was a skinhead and the leader of a violent white supremacist gang that committed acts of racial crime throughout L.A. and his actions greatly influenced Danny. Reformed and fresh out of prison, Derek severs contact with the gang and becomes determined to keep Danny from going down the same violent path as he did.', 2023, 1, 5, 2, '[\"86\",\"154\",\"155\"]', '45', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZVAfE5cT59c', '', '7140'),
(59, 'Neon Genesis Evangelion: The End of Evangelion', 'The second of two theatrically released follow-ups to the Neon Genesis', 'The second of two theatrically released follow-ups to the Neon Genesis Evangelion series. Comprising of two alternate episodes which were first intended to take the place of episodes 25 and 26, this finale answers many of the questions surrounding the series, while also opening up some new possibilities.', 1997, 3, 5, 4, '[\"156\", \"157\", \"158\"]', '46', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Y9cXQfLdGfQ', '', '5220'),
(60, 'The Silence of the Lambs', 'Clarice Starling is a top student at the FBI\'s training academy.  Jack', 'Clarice Starling is a top student at the FBI\'s training academy.  Jack Crawford wants Clarice to interview Dr. Hannibal Lecter, a brilliant psychiatrist who is also a violent psychopath, serving life behind bars for various acts of murder and cannibalism.  Crawford believes that Lecter may have insight into a case and that Starling, as an attractive young woman, may be just the bait to draw him out.', 1991, 1, 4, 13, '[\"159\", \"160\", \"161\"]', '47', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6iB21hsprAQ', '', '7140'),
(61, 'High and Low', 'A shoe company executive who has mortgaged everything he has becomes a', 'A shoe company executive who has mortgaged everything he has becomes a victim of extortion when his chauffeur\'s son is kidnapped and is conflicted over whether he should pay the ransom.', 1963, 3, 4, 13, '[\"59\", \"99\", \"162\"]', '19', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LV3z2Ytxu90', '', '8520'),
(62, 'The Great Dictator', 'Dictator Adenoid Hynkel tries to expand his empire while a poor Jewish', 'Dictator Adenoid Hynkel tries to expand his empire while a poor Jewish barber tries to avoid persecution from Hynkel\'s regime.', 1940, 1, 4, 3, '[\"163\", \"164\", \"165\"]', '48', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=i1C6qZVeFtA', '', '7500'),
(63, 'Princess Mononoke', 'Ashitaka, a prince of the disappearing Emishi people, is cursed by a d', 'Ashitaka, a prince of the disappearing Emishi people, is cursed by a demonized boar god and must journey to the west to find a cure. Along the way, he encounters San, a young human woman fighting to protect the forest, and Lady Eboshi, who is trying to destroy it. Ashitaka must find a way to bring balance to this conflict.', 1997, 3, 4, 9, '[\"166\", \"167\", \"168\"]', '6', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g9k72pqWQsY', '', '8040'),
(64, '20th Century Girl', 'Yeon-du asks her best friend Bora to collect all the information she c', 'Yeon-du asks her best friend Bora to collect all the information she can about Baek Hyun-jin while she is away in the U.S. for heart surgery. Bora decides to get close to Baek\'s best friend, Pung Woon-ho first. However, Bora\'s clumsy plan unfolds in an unexpected direction. In 1999, a year before the new century, Bora, who turns seventeen, falls into the fever of first love.', 2022, 4, 4, 5, '[\"169\", \"170\", \"171\"]', '49', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KFS4_qevE7M', '', '7140'),
(65, 'City Lights', 'In this sound-era silent film, a tramp falls in love with a beautiful ', 'In this sound-era silent film, a tramp falls in love with a beautiful blind flower seller.', 1931, 1, 4, 3, '[\"163\", \"172\", \"173\"]', '48', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7vl7F8S4cpQ', 'https://www.charliechaplin.com/en/films/5-City-Lights', '5220'),
(66, 'Violet Evergarden: The Movie', 'As the world moves on from the war and technological advances bring ch', 'As the world moves on from the war and technological advances bring changes to her life, Violet still hopes to see her lost commanding officer again.', 2020, 3, 4, 4, '[\"174\", \"175\", \"176\"]', '50', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BUfSen2rYQs', 'https://www.netflix.com/title/81193214', '8400'),
(67, 'L?on: The Professional', 'L?on, the top hit man in New York, has earned a rep as an effective \"c', 'L?on, the top hit man in New York, has earned a rep as an effective \"cleaner\". But when his next-door neighbors are wiped out by a loose-cannon DEA agent, he becomes the unwilling custodian of 12-year-old Mathilda. Before long, Mathilda\'s thoughts turn to revenge, and she considers following in L?on\'s footsteps.', 1994, 1, 4, 13, '[\"177\", \"178\", \"179\"]', '51', 1, 0, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PuTe6i8A3Ug', '', '6660');
